menghargaimu!

484
00:31:48,968 --> 00:31:52,038
Apa kau tahu berapa bom yang sudah 
kausebabkan?

485
00:31:52,038 --> 00:31:53,577
Terus mau bagaimana lagi?

486
00:31:53,907 --> 00:31:56,278
Pergilah isi acara radio itu.
Kau tak boleh pergi!

487
00:31:56,278 --> 00:31:58,077
Apa yang kaulakukan?/
Lepas!

488
00:31:58,077 --> 00:32:00,018
Lepas!

489
00:32:00,018 --> 00:32:02,817
Lepas!

490
00:32:03,317 --> 00:32:05,458
