491
00:32:22,137 --> 00:32:24,008
<i>Maaf aku tidak bisa menepati janjiku.</i>

492
00:32:25,407 --> 00:32:27,607
Dasar.

493
00:32:28,107 --> 00:32:31,278
Noona. Bukan, Penulis Song Geu Rim.

494
00:32:33,887 --> 00:32:36,617
Bisa-bisanya dia jadi pergi?

495
00:32:54,067 --> 00:32:56,038
Penutupan yang bagus sekali.

496
00:32:58,607 --> 00:33:00,647
Gara-gara kau, lihat apa yang 
menimpa kita ini.

497
00:33:16,228 --> 00:33:19,998
<i>Aku, Shin Soo Ah, akan mengisi 
selama seminggu ke depan...</i>

498
00:33:19,998 --> 00:33:23,637
