ada sedikit masalah.</i>

499
00:33:23,867 --> 00:33:26,298
<i>Semoga kalian senang denganku.</i>

500
00:33:26,698 --> 00:33:30,308
<i>Banyak sekali yang mengirimkan komentar.</i>

501
00:33:30,438 --> 00:33:32,677
<i>Senang bertemu kalian.</i>

502
00:33:32,677 --> 00:33:35,978
<i>Semoga kalian tak bosan mendengarkan
acara ini sampai tuntas.</i>

503
00:33:36,077 --> 00:33:38,218
<i>Ada banyak hadiah hari ini...,</i>

504
00:33:38,248 --> 00:33:40,617
<i>...jadi tetaplah bersamaku.</i>

505
00:33:40,617 --> 00:33:42,788
<i>Mari kita mulai dengan lagu pertama.</i>

506
00:34:10,478 --> 00:34:12,918
<i>[Mi Nu's Happy 6pm]</i>

507
00:34:25,327 --> 00:34:26,967
