508
00:35:18,717 --> 00:35:21,987
<i>"Sudah saatnya langit biru menjadi jingga."</i>

509
00:35:22,887 --> 00:35:25,518
<i>"Pendengar Mi Nu's Happy 6pm...,"</i>

510
00:35:26,358 --> 00:35:29,358
<i>"...sudah berapa kalian
