625
00:44:04,838 --> 00:44:06,507
Jangan meragukan telingamu.

626
00:44:06,507 --> 00:44:07,808
Kau jelas sekali mendengarnya.

627
00:44:07,947 --> 00:44:09,007
Tapi...

628
00:44:10,378 --> 00:44:13,018
Serius? Ji Soo Ho?

629
00:44:16,487 --> 00:44:21,887
